WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:03.269 line:92%
Guns are my best friends.

00:00:03.302 --> 00:00:05.338
They're cool, they're fun,

00:00:05.371 --> 00:00:08.107
and they've never stabbed me
in the back.

00:00:08.140 --> 00:00:09.942
Except for that one
with the bayonet.

00:00:09.975 --> 00:00:13.579
And for a while, the media was
focused on all the students

00:00:13.612 --> 00:00:16.549
and activists
trying to take my friends away.

00:00:16.582 --> 00:00:18.351
But the news cycle moves fast.

00:00:18.384 --> 00:00:20.019
Today, we're talking so much
about Kanye,

00:00:20.052 --> 00:00:23.589
I can barely remember how many
houses Sean Hannity has (bleep).

00:00:23.622 --> 00:00:25.792
(laughter)

00:00:25.825 --> 00:00:29.295
12, I think... at least.

00:00:29.328 --> 00:00:31.864
But even if the media
has moved on,

00:00:31.897 --> 00:00:34.067
our guns are still
being threatened.

00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:36.269
Don't believe me?
Get a load of this.

