If you want change, save up

00:01:01.160 --> 00:01:03.729
until you can afford a senator,
like everyone else.

00:01:03.762 --> 00:01:05.932
(laughter)

00:01:05.965 --> 00:01:09.402
Opposers, we have to defend
our number one amendment:

00:01:09.435 --> 00:01:11.003
the second one.

00:01:11.036 --> 00:01:13.306
That's why, once again,

00:01:13.339 --> 00:01:16.075
I want to salute
some of our country's

00:01:16.108 --> 00:01:17.777
"Guardians of the Guns."

00:01:17.810 --> 00:01:20.880
-♪ ♪
-(yelling)

00:01:20.913 --> 00:01:23.850
(cheers and applause)

00:01:26.018 --> 00:01:29.388
Our first guardian is singer
Alishia Wolcott,

00:01:29.421 --> 00:01:32.158
who bravely refused to perform
"The National Anthem"

00:01:32.191 --> 00:01:34.026
