her carry a gun on the field.

00:01:38.130 --> 00:01:40.066
And that's a huge sacrifice.

00:01:40.099 --> 00:01:43.302
She could have gained<i> dozen</i>
of new fans from that gig.

00:01:43.335 --> 00:01:45.138
(laughter)

00:01:45.171 --> 00:01:48.574
Besides, baseball needs guns
to stop criminals.

00:01:48.607 --> 00:01:51.744
Do you have any idea how many
bases get stolen each year?

00:01:51.777 --> 00:01:53.446
(laughter)

00:01:53.479 --> 00:01:56.849
Thousands. They've even
given out awards for it.

00:01:56.882 --> 00:01:59.118
In fact...

00:01:59.151 --> 00:02:02.555
(voice breaking): I heard of one
man stealing someone's home.

00:02:02.588 --> 00:02:04.524
(laughter)

00:02:07.760 --> 00:02:09.829
And don't give me any of this

00:02:09.862 --> 00:02:13.299
"You don't need a gun to sing
'The National Anthem'" crap.

00:02:13.332 --> 00:02:16.536
