flamethrower.

00:02:25.611 --> 00:02:27.280
I don't know.

00:02:27.313 --> 00:02:29.115
Here's what liberals
don't understand.

00:02:29.148 --> 00:02:31.684
It's possible to both respect
"The National Anthem,"

00:02:31.717 --> 00:02:34.654
and make a peaceful
political statement.

00:02:34.687 --> 00:02:37.323
See? No, Chuck, not that one.
Not that one, no, no.

00:02:37.356 --> 00:02:39.592
There it is! Yes!

